channel.title: PhyscoScape
channel.description:
[center][b]PhyscoScape[/b][/center] Ok, well the base I used was Back To Basics by Lin. Right now i'm in the beta stages but wanted to release this now that some more stuff has been added so that people find it more things to do.
[center]Features [*] Object Training [*] DeltaScape Pking [*] Working Prayer [*] Added Skiller Area [*] All bars added to shop so you can get smiting up [*] Money increased from what you get from stall [*] More safe areas added. [*] New object to train off of (Bookcase trains mage) [*] XAMPP highscores compatible. [*] XP rates highered [*] Edited some shops added some new things people may like. [/center]
[center]Pictures[/center] [img]http://rapidpik.com/photos/medium/89655-yyfdt.jpg[/img] [img]http://rapidpik.com/photos/medium/89656-6b3qa.jpg[/img] [img]http://rapidpik.com/photos/medium/89657-pg7a6.jpg[/img] [img]http://rapidpik.com/photos/medium/89658-dwspy.jpg[/img] [img]http://rapidpik.com/photos/medium/89659-qng5h.jpg[/img]
